Package: stormr
Title: STORM and Co-STORM Research and Writing Agents for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("James", "User", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "james@example.com"),
    person("OpenAI", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Implements an R-native clone of the STORM and Co-STORM
    research-and-writing workflows using 'ellmer' for LLM orchestration and
    'shinychat' for an interactive Shiny UI. Includes web retrieval tools,
    evidence tracking with citations, mind-map style topic planning, and
    evaluation helpers built on 'vitals'.
